        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Morphological details. (A–D, J) Chilarboreus (Chilarboreus) fossulatus; (E–I, K) Chilarboreus (Pictarboreus) darwini; (A, E) mandible; (B, F) maxilla; (C, G) labium; (D, H) labrum; (I) elytron; (J, K) wing. Abbreviations: lh, laciniar hook (uncus). Scale bars 0.1 mm (A–H), 0.6 mm (I), 0.7 mm (J, K)." ;
